description:
Lipstick Queen founder and beauty storyteller Poppy King is offering up major lip service this episode! But first, we take you inside our slumber party with Charlotte Tilbury, tell you how our new year's resolutions are going, and discuss a new hair gadget presented at the Consumer Electronics Show in Las Vegas.
